<h2 id="130">7. Automatically sending refunds</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>To send refunds automatically, an <a href="/en/orders/managing-orders#1200">order status</a> for credit notes is required. You can use one of the standard statuses or set up your own order status. This status is then only assigned to completed credit notes. These credit notes must not be changed after creation.</p>
